Package magellan.library.impl

Class MagellanCombatSpellImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • magellan.library.impl.MagellanIdentifiableImpl
      • magellan.library.impl.MagellanCombatSpellImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable, java.lang.Comparable<java.lang.Object>, CombatSpell, Identifiable, Unique
    public class MagellanCombatSpellImpl
extends MagellanIdentifiableImpl
implements CombatSpell
    A class representing a combat spell set for a certain unit. It links a unit with a certain spell and contains information at which level the unit wants to cast the spell.
